s.  Most RP types will never be able to see this, most ebay haters will never see this.  <BR>So there you have it. I thank SoE and VI for not doing this sooner.  I've made some pretty good money.  It's been a real job for over a year now.  It's afforded me a nice living and now it's time to move on.  <BR>So for any of you ebay haters remember this.<BR>I have never camped an item in the game to sell.  Only a few people camp to sell on ebay, the real sellers are like me and don't camp.  No money in it.</P><P><BR> </font></td>
