 lack of gear ? no it was the priorities of why they play, you twink for advantage nothing more. What happens when your advantage is lvled out ? you become average and lose ground . Twink by whatever means it to gain advantage when it no longer is an advatage you look for better but after a while there is none and you now need to find if you want to play the game or dress up and play the game :). To each his own that is just my 1.50 on this . </P><P>" Come forth into the darkness my children the Hell I have sown awaits you..." Insaniac Z'Maniac</P><P>Edited by - insaniac on 02/21/2001  14:38:23</font></td>
